data.text: I'm not sure whether the real story behind this photo makes it more or less interesting. A week ago, I posted a photo of two college kids and a bottle of booze who spent the entire night on the steps of the #SacreCoeur in #Paris. This is the girl from that photo about an hour later, falling asleep on the steps of the church and getting a #hug from the municipal worker responsible cleaning up before the morning tourist crowd.
Excellent composition and photostory! Very tenderly!
